        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/mkobach/status/1211336930866188289?s=21",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">When creating a video for social media:<br><br>• You have 1 second to convince someone to watch for 3 seconds<br>• You have 3 seconds to convince someone to watch for 10 seconds <br>• After 10 seconds the narrative needs to convince someone to watch until the end</p>&mdash; Matthew Kobach (@mkobach) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mkobach/status/1211336930866188289?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 29, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
