        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/benwhitelaw/status/1214606880758218752?s=21",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I love <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dennikN?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@dennikN</a>&#39;s end of year infographic. <br><br>This one shows that, for the fifth year in succession, the team wrote fewer articles than the previous year despite having more journalists on staff. <br><br>Less is more. Focus is everything.<br> <a href=\"https://t.co/uu0q3eWmLl\">https://t.co/uu0q3eWmLl</a></p>&mdash; Ben Whitelaw (@benwhitelaw) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/benwhitelaw/status/1214606880758218752?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 7, 2020</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
